      <title>A Lesson from a Naive Binary Search</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/binary-search/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Jun 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>tabularasa8931@gmail.com (Han)</author>
